item.title: CVE-2018-16472|2024-08-05T10:24:32.809Z -- npm -- cached-path-relative
item.description: A prototype pollution attack in cached-path-relative versions <=1.0.1 allows an attacker to inject properties on Object.prototype which are then inherited by all the JS objects through the prototype chain causing a DoS attack.
